metadata.name: Space and Time
metadata.description:
Time is an illusion created by the mind to aid our sense of temporal presence in the vast ocean of space. Time and Space is about feeling overwhelmed by the constant forward march of time. While The clock is ticking, The past increases and the future recedes. We must make the most of every moment, even when our fears get the best.
